data.value:
To register this device,
First click on the Load Data button. It will load the correct data to the required fields.
Click on the CPU combo box and select the correct CPU of this computer have.
Change the RAM capacity as you like. (In this section you only allow to increase the RAM capacity to half of the actual RAM capacity)
Change the Network bandwidth (speed) as you like. Please make sure give the low amount than your actual bandwidth size. Othervise this will full your bandwidth. This field is Mbps scale.
Storage is between the 1GB to 10GB. This storage use by the projects that you contributed. The storage is require from the this PC C drive.
You can add any name to device name.
